Underlay controle plane - OSPF

net add loopback lo ip address 10.0.0.11/32
net add interface swp1 ip address 10.0.0.11/32 
net add interface swp2 ip address 10.0.0.11/32 

net add ospf router-id 10.0.0.11

net add interface swp1 ospf area 0
net add interface swp2 ospf area 0
net add loopback lo ospf area 0

net add interface swp1 ospf network point-to-point
net add interface swp2 ospf network point-to-point


Overlay control plane - BGP EVPN

net add loopback lo ip address 172.16.0.11/32

net add bgp autonomous-system 65000
net add bgp router-id 172.16.0.11

net add bgp neighbor 172.16.0.101 remote-as internal
net add bgp neighbor 172.16.0.102 remote-as internal

net add bgp neighbor 172.16.0.101 update-source 172.16.0.11
net add bgp neighbor 172.16.0.102 update-source 172.16.0.11

net add bgp evpn neighbor 172.16.0.101 route-reflector-client
net add bgp evpn neighbor 172.16.0.102 route-reflector-client

net add bgp evpn neighbor 172.16.0.101 activate
net add bgp evpn neighbor 172.16.0.102 activate

net add bgp evpn advertise-all-vni
